var book = {
	"name": "Proverbs",
	"numChapters": 31,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The proverbs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16402A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16402A\"></sup> of Solomon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16402B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16402B\"></sup> son of David, king of Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16402C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16402C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for gaining wisdom and instruction;for understanding words of insight;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>for receiving instruction in prudent behavior,doing what is right and just and fair;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for giving prudence to those who are simple,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16405D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16405D\"></sup>knowledge and discretion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16405E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16405E\"></sup> to the young—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>let the wise listen and add to their learning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16406F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16406F\"></sup>and let the discerning get guidance—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>for understanding proverbs and parables,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16407G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16407G\"></sup>the sayings and riddles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16407H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16407H\"></sup> of the wise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16407I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16407I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16408J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16408J\"></sup> is the beginning of knowledge,but fools despise wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16408K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16408K\"></sup> and instruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16408L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16408L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Listen, my son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16409M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16409M\"></sup> to your father’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16409N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16409N\"></sup> instructionand do not forsake your mother’s teaching.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16409O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16409O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They are a garland to grace your headand a chain to adorn your neck.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16410P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16410P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My son, if sinful men entice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16411Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16411Q\"></sup> you,do not give in<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16411R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16411R\"></sup> to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16411S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16411S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If they say, “Come along with us;let’s lie in wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16412T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16412T\"></sup> for innocent blood,let’s ambush some harmless soul;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>let’s swallow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16413U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16413U\"></sup> them alive, like the grave,and whole, like those who go down to the pit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16413V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16413V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>we will get all sorts of valuable thingsand fill our houses with plunder;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>cast lots with us;we will all share the loot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16415W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16415W\"></sup>”—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>my son, do not go along with them,do not set foot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16416X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16416X\"></sup> on their paths;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16416Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16416Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for their feet rush into evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16417Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16417Z\"></sup>they are swift to shed blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16417AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16417AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>How useless to spread a netwhere every bird can see it!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>These men lie in wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16419AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16419AB\"></sup> for their own blood;they ambush only themselves!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16419AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16419AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Such are the paths of all who go after ill-gotten gain;it takes away the life of those who get it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16420AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16420AD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Out in the open wisdom calls aloud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16421AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16421AE\"></sup>she raises her voice in the public square;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>on top of the wall she cries out,at the city gate she makes her speech:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“How long will you who are simple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16423AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16423AF\"></sup> love your simple ways?How long will mockers delight in mockeryand fools hate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16423AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16423AG\"></sup> knowledge?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Repent at my rebuke!Then I will pour out my thoughts to you,I will make known to you my teachings.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But since you refuse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16425AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16425AH\"></sup> to listen when I call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16425AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16425AI\"></sup>and no one pays attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16425AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16425AJ\"></sup> when I stretch out my hand,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>since you disregard all my adviceand do not accept my rebuke,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I in turn will laugh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16427AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16427AK\"></sup> when disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16427AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16427AL\"></sup> strikes you;I will mock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16427AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16427AM\"></sup> when calamity overtakes you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16427AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16427AN\"></sup>—",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>when calamity overtakes you like a storm,when disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16428AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16428AO\"></sup> sweeps over you like a whirlwind,when distress and trouble overwhelm you.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Then they will call to me but I will not answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16429AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16429AP\"></sup>they will look for me but will not find me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16429AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16429AQ\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>since they hated knowledgeand did not choose to fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16430AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16430AR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Since they would not accept my adviceand spurned my rebuke,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16431AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16431AS\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>they will eat the fruit of their waysand be filled with the fruit of their schemes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16432AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16432AT\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For the waywardness of the simple will kill them,and the complacency of fools will destroy them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16433AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16433AU\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>but whoever listens to me will live in safety<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16434AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16434AV\"></sup>and be at ease, without fear of harm.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16434AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16434AW\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16435A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16435A\"></sup> if you accept my wordsand store up my commands within you,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>turning your ear to wisdomand applying your heart to understanding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16436B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16436B\"></sup>—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>indeed, if you call out for insight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16437C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16437C\"></sup>and cry aloud for understanding,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and if you look for it as for silverand search for it as for hidden treasure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16438D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16438D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>then you will understand the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and find the knowledge of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16439E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16439E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives wisdom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16440F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16440F\"></sup>from his mouth come knowledge and understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16440G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16440G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He holds success in store for the upright,he is a shield<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16441H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16441H\"></sup> to those whose walk is blameless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16441I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16441I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for he guards the course of the justand protects the way of his faithful ones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16442J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16442J\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then you will understand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16443K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16443K\"></sup> what is right and justand fair—every good path.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For wisdom will enter your heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16444L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16444L\"></sup>and knowledge will be pleasant to your soul.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Discretion will protect you,and understanding will guard you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16445M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16445M\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Wisdom will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16446N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16446N\"></sup> you from the ways of wicked men,from men whose words are perverse,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>who have left the straight pathsto walk in dark ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16447O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16447O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>who delight in doing wrongand rejoice in the perverseness of evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16448P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16448P\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>whose paths are crooked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16449Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16449Q\"></sup>and who are devious in their ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16449R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16449R\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Wisdom will save you also from the adulterous woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16450S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16450S\"></sup>from the wayward woman with her seductive words,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>who has left the partner of her youthand ignored the covenant she made before God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16451T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16451T\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Surely her house leads down to deathand her paths to the spirits of the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16452U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16452U\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>None who go to her returnor attain the paths of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16453V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16453V\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Thus you will walk in the ways of the goodand keep to the paths of the righteous.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the upright will live in the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16455W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16455W\"></sup>and the blameless will remain in it;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>but the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16456X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16456X\"></sup> will be cut off from the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16456Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16456Y\"></sup>and the unfaithful will be torn from it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16456Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16456Z\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16457A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16457A\"></sup> do not forget my teaching,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16457B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16457B\"></sup>but keep my commands in your heart,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for they will prolong your life many years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16458C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16458C\"></sup>and bring you peace and prosperity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16458D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16458D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let love and faithfulness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16459E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16459E\"></sup> never leave you;bind them around your neck,write them on the tablet of your heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16459F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16459F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then you will win favor and a good namein the sight of God and man.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16460G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16460G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16461H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16461H\"></sup> with all your heartand lean not on your own understanding;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>in all your ways submit to him,and he will make your paths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16462I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16462I\"></sup> straight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16462J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16462J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Do not be wise in your own eyes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16463K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16463K\"></sup>fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16463L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16463L\"></sup> and shun evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16463M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16463M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This will bring health to your body<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16464N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16464N\"></sup>and nourishment to your bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16464O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16464O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Honor the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with your wealth,with the firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16465P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16465P\"></sup> of all your crops;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>then your barns will be filled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16466Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16466Q\"></sup> to overflowing,and your vats will brim over with new wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16466R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16466R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16467S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16467S\"></sup> do not despise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s discipline,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16467T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16467T\"></sup>and do not resent his rebuke,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> disciplines those he loves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16468U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16468U\"></sup>as a father the son he delights in.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16468V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16468V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Blessed are those who find wisdom,those who gain understanding,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>for she is more profitable than silverand yields better returns than gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16470W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16470W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>She is more precious than rubies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16471X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16471X\"></sup>nothing you desire can compare with her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16471Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16471Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Long life is in her right hand;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16472Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16472Z\"></sup>in her left hand are riches and honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16472AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16472AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Her ways are pleasant ways,and all her paths are peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16473AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16473AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She is a tree of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16474AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16474AC\"></sup> to those who take hold of her;those who hold her fast will be blessed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16474AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16474AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>By wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16475AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16475AE\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> laid the earth’s foundations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16475AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16475AF\"></sup>by understanding he set the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16475AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16475AG\"></sup> in place;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>by his knowledge the watery depths were divided,and the clouds let drop the dew.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16477AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16477AH\"></sup> do not let wisdom and understanding out of your sight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16477AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16477AI\"></sup>preserve sound judgment and discretion;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>they will be life for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16478AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16478AJ\"></sup>an ornament to grace your neck.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16478AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16478AK\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then you will go on your way in safety,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16479AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16479AL\"></sup>and your foot will not stumble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16479AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16479AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When you lie down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16480AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16480AN\"></sup> you will not be afraid;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16480AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16480AO\"></sup>when you lie down, your sleep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16480AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16480AP\"></sup> will be sweet.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Have no fear of sudden disasteror of the ruin that overtakes the wicked,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be at your side<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16482AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16482AQ\"></sup>and will keep your foot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16482AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16482AR\"></sup> from being snared.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16482AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16482AS\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Do not withhold good from those to whom it is due,when it is in your power to act.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not say to your neighbor,“Come back tomorrow and I’ll give it to you”—when you already have it with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16484AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16484AT\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do not plot harm against your neighbor,who lives trustfully near you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16485AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16485AU\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Do not accuse anyone for no reason—when they have done you no harm.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Do not envy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16487AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16487AV\"></sup> the violentor choose any of their ways.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests the perverse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16488AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16488AW\"></sup>but takes the upright into his confidence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16488AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16488AX\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16489AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16489AY\"></sup> is on the house of the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16489AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16489AZ\"></sup>but he blesses the home of the righteous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16489BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16489BA\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He mocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16490BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16490BB\"></sup> proud mockers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16490BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16490BC\"></sup>but shows favor to the humble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16490BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16490BD\"></sup> and oppressed.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The wise inherit honor,but fools get only shame."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Listen, my sons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16492A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16492A\"></sup> to a father’s instruction;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16492B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16492B\"></sup>pay attention and gain understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16492C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16492C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I give you sound learning,so do not forsake my teaching.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For I too was a son to my father,still tender, and cherished by my mother.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then he taught me, and he said to me,“Take hold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16495D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16495D\"></sup> of my words with all your heart;keep my commands, and you will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16495E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16495E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Get wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16496F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16496F\"></sup> get understanding;do not forget my words or turn away from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not forsake wisdom, and she will protect you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16497G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16497G\"></sup>love her, and she will watch over you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16497H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16497H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The beginning of wisdom is this: Get wisdom.Though it cost all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16498I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16498I\"></sup> you have, get understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16498J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16498J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Cherish her, and she will exalt you;embrace her, and she will honor you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16499K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16499K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>She will give you a garland to grace your headand present you with a glorious crown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16500L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16500L\"></sup>”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Listen, my son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16501M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16501M\"></sup> accept what I say,and the years of your life will be many.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16501N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16501N\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I instruct<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16502O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16502O\"></sup> you in the way of wisdomand lead you along straight paths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16502P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16502P\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you walk, your steps will not be hampered;when you run, you will not stumble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16503Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16503Q\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Hold on to instruction, do not let it go;guard it well, for it is your life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16504R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16504R\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not set foot on the path of the wickedor walk in the way of evildoers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16505S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16505S\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Avoid it, do not travel on it;turn from it and go on your way.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For they cannot rest until they do evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16507T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16507T\"></sup>they are robbed of sleep till they make someone stumble.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They eat the bread of wickednessand drink the wine of violence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16508U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16508U\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The path of the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16509V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16509V\"></sup> is like the morning sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16509W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16509W\"></sup>shining ever brighter till the full light of day.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16509X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16509X\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But the way of the wicked is like deep darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16510Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16510Y\"></sup>they do not know what makes them stumble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16510Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16510Z\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16511AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16511AA\"></sup> pay attention to what I say;turn your ear to my words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16511AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16511AB\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not let them out of your sight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16512AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16512AC\"></sup>keep them within your heart;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for they are life to those who find themand health to one’s whole body.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16513AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16513AD\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Above all else, guard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16514AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16514AE\"></sup> your heart,for everything you do flows from it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16514AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16514AF\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Keep your mouth free of perversity;keep corrupt talk far from your lips.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let your eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16516AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16516AG\"></sup> look straight ahead;fix your gaze directly before you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Give careful thought to the paths for your feet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16517AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16517AH\"></sup>and be steadfast in all your ways.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Do not turn to the right or the left;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16518AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16518AI\"></sup>keep your foot from evil."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16519A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16519A\"></sup> pay attention to my wisdom,turn your ear to my words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16519B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16519B\"></sup> of insight,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>that you may maintain discretionand your lips may preserve knowledge.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the lips of the adulterous woman drip honey,and her speech is smoother than oil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16521C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16521C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but in the end she is bitter as gall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16522D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16522D\"></sup>sharp as a double-edged sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Her feet go down to death;her steps lead straight to the grave.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16523E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16523E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>She gives no thought to the way of life;her paths wander aimlessly, but she does not know it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16524F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16524F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now then, my sons, listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16525G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16525G\"></sup> to me;do not turn aside from what I say.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Keep to a path far from her,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16526H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16526H\"></sup>do not go near the door of her house,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>lest you lose your honor to othersand your dignity to one who is cruel,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>lest strangers feast on your wealthand your toil enrich the house of another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16528I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16528I\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>At the end of your life you will groan,when your flesh and body are spent.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You will say, “How I hated discipline!How my heart spurned correction!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16530J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16530J\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I would not obey my teachersor turn my ear to my instructors.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And I was soon in serious trouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16532K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16532K\"></sup>in the assembly of God’s people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16532L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16532L\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Drink water from your own cistern,running water from your own well.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Should your springs overflow in the streets,your streams of water in the public squares?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let them be yours alone,never to be shared with strangers.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>May your fountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16536M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16536M\"></sup> be blessed,and may you rejoice in the wife of your youth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16536N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16536N\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A loving doe, a graceful deer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16537O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16537O\"></sup>—may her breasts satisfy you always,may you ever be intoxicated with her love.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Why, my son, be intoxicated with another man’s wife?Why embrace the bosom of a wayward woman?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For your ways are in full view<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16539P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16539P\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and he examines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16539Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16539Q\"></sup> all your paths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16539R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16539R\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The evil deeds of the wicked ensnare them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16540S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16540S\"></sup>the cords of their sins hold them fast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16540T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16540T\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For lack of discipline they will die,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16541U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16541U\"></sup>led astray by their own great folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16541V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16541V\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16542A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16542A\"></sup> if you have put up security<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16542B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16542B\"></sup> for your neighbor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16542C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16542C\"></sup>if you have shaken hands in pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16542D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16542D\"></sup> for a stranger,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>you have been trapped by what you said,ensnared by the words of your mouth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So do this, my son, to free yourself,since you have fallen into your neighbor’s hands:Go—to the point of exhaustion—and give your neighbor no rest!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Allow no sleep to your eyes,no slumber to your eyelids.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16545E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16545E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Free yourself, like a gazelle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16546F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16546F\"></sup> from the hand of the hunter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16546G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16546G\"></sup>like a bird from the snare of the fowler.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16546H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16546H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Go to the ant, you sluggard;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16547I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16547I\"></sup>consider its ways and be wise!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It has no commander,no overseer or ruler,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>yet it stores its provisions in summer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16549J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16549J\"></sup>and gathers its food at harvest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16549K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16549K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>How long will you lie there, you sluggard?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16550L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16550L\"></sup>When will you get up from your sleep?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A little sleep, a little slumber,a little folding of the hands to rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16551M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16551M\"></sup>—",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and poverty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16552N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16552N\"></sup> will come on you like a thiefand scarcity like an armed man.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A troublemaker and a villain,who goes about with a corrupt mouth,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>who winks maliciously with his eye,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16554O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16554O\"></sup>signals with his feetand motions with his fingers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16554P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16554P\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>who plots evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16555Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16555Q\"></sup> with deceit in his heart—he always stirs up conflict.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16555R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16555R\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore disaster will overtake him in an instant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16556S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16556S\"></sup>he will suddenly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16556T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16556T\"></sup> be destroyed—without remedy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16556U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16556U\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>There are six things the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hates,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16557V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16557V\"></sup>seven that are detestable to him:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span class=\"indent-2-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>haughty eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16558W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16558W\"></sup>a lying tongue,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16558X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16558X\"></sup>hands that shed innocent blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16558Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16558Y\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><span class=\"indent-2-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>a heart that devises wicked schemes,feet that are quick to rush into evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16559Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16559Z\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><span class=\"indent-2-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>a false witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16560AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16560AA\"></sup> who pours out lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16560AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16560AB\"></sup>and a person who stirs up conflict in the community.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16560AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16560AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16561AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16561AD\"></sup> keep your father’s commandand do not forsake your mother’s teaching.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16561AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16561AE\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Bind them always on your heart;fasten them around your neck.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16562AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16562AF\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When you walk, they will guide you;when you sleep, they will watch over you;when you awake, they will speak to you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For this command is a lamp,this teaching is a light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16564AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16564AG\"></sup>and correction and instructionare the way to life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16564AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16564AH\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>keeping you from your neighbor’s wife,from the smooth talk of a wayward woman.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16565AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16565AI\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Do not lust in your heart after her beautyor let her captivate you with her eyes.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For a prostitute can be had for a loaf of bread,but another man’s wife preys on your very life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16567AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16567AJ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Can a man scoop fire into his lapwithout his clothes being burned?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Can a man walk on hot coalswithout his feet being scorched?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So is he who sleeps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16570AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16570AK\"></sup> with another man’s wife;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16570AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16570AL\"></sup>no one who touches her will go unpunished.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>People do not despise a thief if he stealsto satisfy his hunger when he is starving.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Yet if he is caught, he must pay sevenfold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16572AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16572AM\"></sup>though it costs him all the wealth of his house.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But a man who commits adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16573AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16573AN\"></sup> has no sense;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16573AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16573AO\"></sup>whoever does so destroys himself.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Blows and disgrace are his lot,and his shame will never<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16574AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16574AP\"></sup> be wiped away.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For jealousy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16575AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16575AQ\"></sup> arouses a husband’s fury,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16575AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16575AR\"></sup>and he will show no mercy when he takes revenge.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>He will not accept any compensation;he will refuse a bribe, however great it is.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16576AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16576AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16577A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16577A\"></sup> keep my wordsand store up my commands within you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Keep my commands and you will live;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16578B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16578B\"></sup>guard my teachings as the apple of your eye.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Bind them on your fingers;write them on the tablet of your heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16579C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16579C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to wisdom, “You are my sister,”and to insight, “You are my relative.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They will keep you from the adulterous woman,from the wayward woman with her seductive words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16581D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16581D\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>At the window of my houseI looked down through the lattice.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I saw among the simple,I noticed among the young men,a youth who had no sense.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16583E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16583E\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He was going down the street near her corner,walking along in the direction of her house",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>at twilight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16585F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16585F\"></sup> as the day was fading,as the dark of night set in.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then out came a woman to meet him,dressed like a prostitute and with crafty intent.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>(She is unruly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16587G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16587G\"></sup> and defiant,her feet never stay at home;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>now in the street, now in the squares,at every corner she lurks.)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16588H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16588H\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She took hold of him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16589I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16589I\"></sup> and kissed himand with a brazen face she said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16589J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16589J\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Today I fulfilled my vows,and I have food from my fellowship offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16590K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16590K\"></sup> at home.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So I came out to meet you;I looked for you and have found you!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have covered my bedwith colored linens from Egypt.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I have perfumed my bed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16593L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16593L\"></sup>with myrrh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16593M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16593M\"></sup> aloes and cinnamon.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Come, let’s drink deeply of love till morning;let’s enjoy ourselves with love!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16594N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16594N\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>My husband is not at home;he has gone on a long journey.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He took his purse filled with moneyand will not be home till full moon.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>With persuasive words she led him astray;she seduced him with her smooth talk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16597O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16597O\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>All at once he followed herlike an ox going to the slaughter,like a deer stepping into a noose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16598P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16598P\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>till an arrow pierces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16599Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16599Q\"></sup> his liver,like a bird darting into a snare,little knowing it will cost him his life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16599R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16599R\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now then, my sons, listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16600S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16600S\"></sup> to me;pay attention to what I say.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Do not let your heart turn to her waysor stray into her paths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16601T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16601T\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Many are the victims she has brought down;her slain are a mighty throng.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Her house is a highway to the grave,leading down to the chambers of death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16603U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16603U\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Does not wisdom call out?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16604A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16604A\"></sup>Does not understanding raise her voice?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>At the highest point along the way,where the paths meet, she takes her stand;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>beside the gate leading into the city,at the entrance, she cries aloud:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16606B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16606B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“To you, O people, I call out;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16607C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16607C\"></sup>I raise my voice to all mankind.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You who are simple,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16608D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16608D\"></sup> gain prudence;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16608E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16608E\"></sup>you who are foolish, set your hearts on it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Listen, for I have trustworthy things to say;I open my lips to speak what is right.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>My mouth speaks what is true,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16610F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16610F\"></sup>for my lips detest wickedness.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All the words of my mouth are just;none of them is crooked or perverse.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>To the discerning all of them are right;they are upright to those who have found knowledge.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Choose my instruction instead of silver,knowledge rather than choice gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16613G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16613G\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>for wisdom is more precious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16614H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16614H\"></sup> than rubies,and nothing you desire can compare with her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16614I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16614I\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I, wisdom, dwell together with prudence;I possess knowledge and discretion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16615J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16615J\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>To fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16616K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16616K\"></sup> is to hate evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16616L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16616L\"></sup>I hate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16616M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16616M\"></sup> pride and arrogance,evil behavior and perverse speech.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Counsel and sound judgment are mine;I have insight, I have power.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16617N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16617N\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>By me kings reignand rulers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16618O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16618O\"></sup> issue decrees that are just;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>by me princes govern,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16619P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16619P\"></sup>and nobles—all who rule on earth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I love those who love me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16620Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16620Q\"></sup>and those who seek me find me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16620R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16620R\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>With me are riches and honor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16621S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16621S\"></sup>enduring wealth and prosperity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16621T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16621T\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>My fruit is better than fine gold;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16622U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16622U\"></sup>what I yield surpasses choice silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16622V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16622V\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I walk in the way of righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16623W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16623W\"></sup>along the paths of justice,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>bestowing a rich inheritance on those who love meand making their treasuries full.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16624X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16624X\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> brought me forth as the first of his works,before his deeds of old;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I was formed long ages ago,at the very beginning, when the world came to be.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When there were no watery depths, I was given birth,when there were no springs overflowing with water;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16627Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16627Y\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>before the mountains were settled in place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16628Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16628Z\"></sup>before the hills, I was given birth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16628AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16628AA\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>before he made the world or its fieldsor any of the dust of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16629AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16629AB\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>I was there when he set the heavens in place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16630AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16630AC\"></sup>when he marked out the horizon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16630AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16630AD\"></sup> on the face of the deep,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>when he established the clouds above<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16631AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16631AE\"></sup>and fixed securely the fountains of the deep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16631AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16631AF\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>when he gave the sea its boundary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16632AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16632AG\"></sup>so the waters would not overstep his command,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16632AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16632AH\"></sup>and when he marked out the foundations of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16632AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16632AI\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Then I was constantly at his side.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16633AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16633AJ\"></sup>I was filled with delight day after day,rejoicing always in his presence,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>rejoicing in his whole worldand delighting in mankind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16634AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16634AK\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Now then, my children, listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16635AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16635AL\"></sup> to me;blessed are<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16635AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16635AM\"></sup> those who keep my ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16635AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16635AN\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Listen to my instruction and be wise;do not disregard it.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Blessed are those who listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16637AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16637AO\"></sup> to me,watching daily at my doors,waiting at my doorway.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For those who find me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16638AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16638AP\"></sup> find life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16638AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16638AQ\"></sup>and receive favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16638AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16638AR\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But those who fail to find me harm themselves;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16639AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16639AS\"></sup>all who hate me love death.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16639AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16639AT\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Wisdom has built<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16640A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16640A\"></sup> her house;she has set up its seven pillars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>She has prepared her meat and mixed her wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16641B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16641B\"></sup>she has also set her table.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16641C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16641C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>She has sent out her servants, and she calls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16642D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16642D\"></sup>from the highest point of the city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16642E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16642E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>“Let all who are simple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16643F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16643F\"></sup> come to my house!”To those who have no sense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16643G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16643G\"></sup> she says,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>“Come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16644H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16644H\"></sup> eat my foodand drink the wine I have mixed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16644I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16644I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Leave your simple ways and you will live;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16645J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16645J\"></sup>walk in the way of insight.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16645K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16645K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Whoever corrects a mocker invites insults;whoever rebukes the wicked incurs abuse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16646L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16646L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do not rebuke mockers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16647M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16647M\"></sup> or they will hate you;rebuke the wise and they will love you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16647N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16647N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Instruct the wise and they will be wiser still;teach the righteous and they will add to their learning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16648O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16648O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16649P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16649P\"></sup> is the beginning of wisdom,and knowledge of the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16649Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16649Q\"></sup> is understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16649R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16649R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For through wisdom your days will be many,and years will be added to your life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16650S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16650S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you are wise, your wisdom will reward you;if you are a mocker, you alone will suffer.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Folly is an unruly woman;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16652T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16652T\"></sup>she is simple and knows nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16652U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16652U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She sits at the door of her house,on a seat at the highest point of the city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16653V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16653V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>calling out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16654W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16654W\"></sup> to those who pass by,who go straight on their way,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>“Let all who are simple come to my house!”To those who have no sense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16655X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16655X\"></sup> she says,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>“Stolen water is sweet;food eaten in secret is delicious!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16656Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16656Y\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But little do they know that the dead are there,that her guests are deep in the realm of the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16657Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16657Z\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>The proverbs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16658A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16658A\"></sup> of Solomon:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16658B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16658B\"></sup>A wise son brings joy to his father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16658C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16658C\"></sup>but a foolish son brings grief to his mother.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Ill-gotten treasures have no lasting value,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16659D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16659D\"></sup>but righteousness delivers from death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16659E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16659E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not let the righteous go hungry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16660F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16660F\"></sup>but he thwarts the craving of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16660G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16660G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Lazy hands make for poverty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16661H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16661H\"></sup>but diligent hands bring wealth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16661I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16661I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who gathers crops in summer is a prudent son,but he who sleeps during harvest is a disgraceful son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16662J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16662J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Blessings crown the head of the righteous,but violence overwhelms the mouth of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16663K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16663K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The name of the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16664L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16664L\"></sup> is used in blessings,but the name of the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16664M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16664M\"></sup> will rot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16664N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The wise in heart accept commands,but a chattering fool comes to ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16665O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16665O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever walks in integrity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16666P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16666P\"></sup> walks securely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16666Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16666Q\"></sup>but whoever takes crooked paths will be found out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16666R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16666R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever winks maliciously<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16667S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16667S\"></sup> causes grief,and a chattering fool comes to ruin.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The mouth of the righteous is a fountain of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16668T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16668T\"></sup>but the mouth of the wicked conceals violence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16668U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16668U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Hatred stirs up conflict,but love covers over all wrongs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16669V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Wisdom is found on the lips of the discerning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16670W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16670W\"></sup>but a rod is for the back of one who has no sense.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16670X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16670X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The wise store up knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16671Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16671Y\"></sup>but the mouth of a fool invites ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16671Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16671Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The wealth of the rich is their fortified city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16672AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16672AA\"></sup>but poverty is the ruin of the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16672AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16672AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The wages of the righteous is life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16673AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16673AC\"></sup>but the earnings of the wicked are sin and death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16673AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16673AD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever heeds discipline shows the way to life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16674AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16674AE\"></sup>but whoever ignores correction leads others astray.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Whoever conceals hatred with lying lips<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16675AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16675AF\"></sup>and spreads slander is a fool.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Sin is not ended by multiplying words,but the prudent hold their tongues.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16676AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16676AG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The tongue of the righteous is choice silver,but the heart of the wicked is of little value.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The lips of the righteous nourish many,but fools die for lack of sense.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16678AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16678AH\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The blessing of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16679AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16679AI\"></sup> brings wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16679AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16679AJ\"></sup>without painful toil for it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16679AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16679AK\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A fool finds pleasure in wicked schemes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16680AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16680AL\"></sup>but a person of understanding delights in wisdom.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>What the wicked dread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16681AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16681AM\"></sup> will overtake them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16681AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16681AN\"></sup>what the righteous desire will be granted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16681AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16681AO\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When the storm has swept by, the wicked are gone,but the righteous stand firm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16682AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16682AP\"></sup> forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16682AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16682AQ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>As vinegar to the teeth and smoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16683AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16683AR\"></sup> to the eyes,so are sluggards to those who send them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16683AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16683AS\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> adds length to life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16684AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16684AT\"></sup>but the years of the wicked are cut short.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16684AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16684AU\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The prospect of the righteous is joy,but the hopes of the wicked come to nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16685AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16685AV\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a refuge for the blameless,but it is the ruin of those who do evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16686AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16686AW\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The righteous will never be uprooted,but the wicked will not remain in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16687AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16687AX\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>From the mouth of the righteous comes the fruit of wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16688AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16688AY\"></sup>but a perverse tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16688AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16688AZ\"></sup> will be silenced.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The lips of the righteous know what finds favor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16689BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16689BA\"></sup>but the mouth of the wicked only what is perverse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16689BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16689BB\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests dishonest scales,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16690A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16690A\"></sup>but accurate weights find favor with him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16690B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16690B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When pride comes, then comes disgrace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16691C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16691C\"></sup>but with humility comes wisdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16691D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16691D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The integrity of the upright guides them,but the unfaithful are destroyed by their duplicity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16692E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16692E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16693F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16693F\"></sup> is worthless in the day of wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16693G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16693G\"></sup>but righteousness delivers from death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16693H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16693H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The righteousness of the blameless makes their paths straight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16694I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16694I\"></sup>but the wicked are brought down by their own wickedness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16694J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16694J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The righteousness of the upright delivers them,but the unfaithful are trapped by evil desires.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16695K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16695K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Hopes placed in mortals die with them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16696L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16696L\"></sup>all the promise of their power comes to nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16696M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16696M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The righteous person is rescued from trouble,and it falls on the wicked instead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16697N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16697N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>With their mouths the godless destroy their neighbors,but through knowledge the righteous escape.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16698O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16698O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When the righteous prosper, the city rejoices;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16699P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16699P\"></sup>when the wicked perish, there are shouts of joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16699Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16699Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Through the blessing of the upright a city is exalted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16700R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16700R\"></sup>but by the mouth of the wicked it is destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16700S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16700S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Whoever derides their neighbor has no sense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16701T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16701T\"></sup>but the one who has understanding holds their tongue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16701U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16701U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A gossip betrays a confidence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16702V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16702V\"></sup>but a trustworthy person keeps a secret.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16702W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16702W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For lack of guidance a nation falls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16703X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16703X\"></sup>but victory is won through many advisers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16703Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16703Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Whoever puts up security<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16704Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16704Z\"></sup> for a stranger will surely suffer,but whoever refuses to shake hands in pledge is safe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16704AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16704AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A kindhearted woman gains honor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16705AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16705AB\"></sup>but ruthless men gain only wealth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Those who are kind benefit themselves,but the cruel bring ruin on themselves.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A wicked person earns deceptive wages,but the one who sows righteousness reaps a sure reward.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16707AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16707AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Truly the righteous attain life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16708AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16708AD\"></sup>but whoever pursues evil finds death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16708AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16708AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests those whose hearts are perverse,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16709AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16709AF\"></sup>but he delights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16709AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16709AG\"></sup> in those whose ways are blameless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16709AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16709AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Be sure of this: The wicked will not go unpunished,but those who are righteous will go free.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16710AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16710AI\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Like a gold ring in a pig’s snoutis a beautiful woman who shows no discretion.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The desire of the righteous ends only in good,but the hope of the wicked only in wrath.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>One person gives freely, yet gains even more;another withholds unduly, but comes to poverty.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A generous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16714AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16714AJ\"></sup> person will prosper;whoever refreshes others will be refreshed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16714AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16714AK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>People curse the one who hoards grain,but they pray God’s blessing on the one who is willing to sell.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whoever seeks good finds favor,but evil comes to one who searches for it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16716AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16716AL\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Those who trust in their riches will fall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16717AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16717AM\"></sup>but the righteous will thrive like a green leaf.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16717AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16717AN\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Whoever brings ruin on their family will inherit only wind,and the fool will be servant to the wise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16718AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16718AO\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The fruit of the righteous is a tree of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16719AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16719AP\"></sup>and the one who is wise saves lives.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>If the righteous receive their due<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16720AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16720AQ\"></sup> on earth,how much more the ungodly and the sinner!"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Whoever loves discipline loves knowledge,but whoever hates correction is stupid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16721A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16721A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Good people obtain favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16722B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16722B\"></sup>but he condemns those who devise wicked schemes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16722C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16722C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>No one can be established through wickedness,but the righteous cannot be uprooted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16723D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16723D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A wife of noble character<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16724E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16724E\"></sup> is her husband’s crown,but a disgraceful wife is like decay in his bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16724F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16724F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The plans of the righteous are just,but the advice of the wicked is deceitful.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The words of the wicked lie in wait for blood,but the speech of the upright rescues them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16726G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16726G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The wicked are overthrown and are no more,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16727H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16727H\"></sup>but the house of the righteous stands firm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16727I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16727I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A person is praised according to their prudence,and one with a warped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16728J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16728J\"></sup> mind is despised.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Better to be a nobody and yet have a servantthan pretend to be somebody and have no food.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The righteous care for the needs of their animals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16730K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16730K\"></sup>but the kindest acts of the wicked are cruel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Those who work their land will have abundant food,but those who chase fantasies have no sense.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16731L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16731L\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The wicked desire the stronghold of evildoers,but the root of the righteous endures.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Evildoers are trapped by their sinful talk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16733M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16733M\"></sup>and so the innocent escape trouble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16733N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16733N\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>From the fruit of their lips people are filled with good things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16734O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16734O\"></sup>and the work of their hands brings them reward.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16734P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16734P\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The way of fools seems right to them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16735Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16735Q\"></sup>but the wise listen to advice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16735R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16735R\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Fools<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16736S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16736S\"></sup> show their annoyance at once,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16736T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16736T\"></sup>but the prudent overlook an insult.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16736U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16736U\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>An honest witness tells the truth,but a false witness tells lies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16737V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16737V\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The words of the reckless pierce like swords,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16738W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16738W\"></sup>but the tongue of the wise brings healing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16738X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16738X\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Truthful lips endure forever,but a lying tongue lasts only a moment.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Deceit is in the hearts of those who plot evil,but those who promote peace have joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16740Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16740Y\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>No harm overtakes the righteous,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16741Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16741Z\"></sup>but the wicked have their fill of trouble.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests lying lips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16742AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16742AA\"></sup>but he delights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16742AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16742AB\"></sup> in people who are trustworthy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16742AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16742AC\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The prudent keep their knowledge to themselves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16743AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16743AD\"></sup>but a fool’s heart blurts out folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16743AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16743AE\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Diligent hands will rule,but laziness ends in forced labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16744AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16744AF\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Anxiety weighs down the heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16745AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16745AG\"></sup>but a kind word cheers it up.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The righteous choose their friends carefully,but the way of the wicked leads them astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16746AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16746AH\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The lazy do not roast any game,but the diligent feed on the riches of the hunt.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In the way of righteousness there is life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16748AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16748AI\"></sup>along that path is immortality."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>A wise son heeds his father’s instruction,but a mocker does not respond to rebukes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16749A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>From the fruit of their lips people enjoy good things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16750B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16750B\"></sup>but the unfaithful have an appetite for violence.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Those who guard their lips<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16751C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16751C\"></sup> preserve their lives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16751D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16751D\"></sup>but those who speak rashly will come to ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16751E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16751E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A sluggard’s appetite is never filled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16752F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16752F\"></sup>but the desires of the diligent are fully satisfied.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The righteous hate what is false,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16753G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16753G\"></sup>but the wicked make themselves a stenchand bring shame on themselves.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Righteousness guards the person of integrity,but wickedness overthrows the sinner.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16754H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16754H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>One person pretends to be rich, yet has nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16755I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16755I\"></sup>another pretends to be poor, yet has great wealth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16755J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16755J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A person’s riches may ransom their life,but the poor cannot respond to threatening rebukes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16756K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16756K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The light of the righteous shines brightly,but the lamp of the wicked is snuffed out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16757L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16757L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Where there is strife, there is pride,but wisdom is found in those who take advice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16758M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16758M\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Dishonest money dwindles away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16759N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16759N\"></sup>but whoever gathers money little by little makes it grow.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Hope deferred makes the heart sick,but a longing fulfilled is a tree of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16760O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16760O\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever scorns instruction will pay for it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16761P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16761P\"></sup>but whoever respects<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16761Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16761Q\"></sup> a command is rewarded.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16761R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16761R\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The teaching of the wise is a fountain of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16762S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16762S\"></sup>turning a person from the snares of death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16762T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16762T\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Good judgment wins favor,but the way of the unfaithful leads to their destruction.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>All who are prudent act with knowledge,but fools expose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16764U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16764U\"></sup> their folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16764V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16764V\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A wicked messenger falls into trouble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16765W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16765W\"></sup>but a trustworthy envoy brings healing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16765X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16765X\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Whoever disregards discipline comes to poverty and shame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16766Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16766Y\"></sup>but whoever heeds correction is honored.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16766Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16766Z\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A longing fulfilled is sweet to the soul,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16767AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16767AA\"></sup>but fools detest turning from evil.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Walk with the wise and become wise,for a companion of fools suffers harm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16768AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16768AB\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Trouble pursues the sinner,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16769AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16769AC\"></sup>but the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16769AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16769AD\"></sup> are rewarded with good things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16769AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16769AE\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A good person leaves an inheritance for their children’s children,but a sinner’s wealth is stored up for the righteous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16770AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16770AF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>An unplowed field produces food for the poor,but injustice sweeps it away.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever spares the rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16772AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16772AG\"></sup> hates their children,but the one who loves their children is careful to discipline<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16772AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16772AH\"></sup> them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16772AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16772AI\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The righteous eat to their hearts’ content,but the stomach of the wicked goes hungry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16773AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16773AJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>The wise woman builds her house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16774A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16774A\"></sup>but with her own hands the foolish one tears hers down.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Whoever fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> walks uprightly,but those who despise him are devious in their ways.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A fool’s mouth lashes out with pride,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16776B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16776B\"></sup>but the lips of the wise protect them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16776C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16776C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Where there are no oxen, the manger is empty,but from the strength of an ox<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16777D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16777D\"></sup> come abundant harvests.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>An honest witness does not deceive,but a false witness pours out lies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16778E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16778E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The mocker seeks wisdom and finds none,but knowledge comes easily to the discerning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16779F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16779F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Stay away from a fool,for you will not find knowledge on their lips.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The wisdom of the prudent is to give thought to their ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16781G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16781G\"></sup>but the folly of fools is deception.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16781H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16781H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Fools mock at making amends for sin,but goodwill is found among the upright.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Each heart knows its own bitterness,and no one else can share its joy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The house of the wicked will be destroyed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16784I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16784I\"></sup>but the tent of the upright will flourish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16784J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16784J\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There is a way that appears to be right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16785K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16785K\"></sup>but in the end it leads to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16785L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16785L\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even in laughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16786M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16786M\"></sup> the heart may ache,and rejoicing may end in grief.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The faithless will be fully repaid for their ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16787N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16787N\"></sup>and the good rewarded for theirs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16787O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16787O\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The simple believe anything,but the prudent give thought to their steps.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16788P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16788P\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The wise fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and shun evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16789Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16789Q\"></sup>but a fool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16789R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16789R\"></sup> is hotheaded and yet feels secure.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A quick-tempered person<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16790S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16790S\"></sup> does foolish things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16790T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16790T\"></sup>and the one who devises evil schemes is hated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16790U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16790U\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The simple inherit folly,but the prudent are crowned with knowledge.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Evildoers will bow down in the presence of the good,and the wicked at the gates of the righteous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16792V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16792V\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The poor are shunned even by their neighbors,but the rich have many friends.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16793W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16793W\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It is a sin to despise one’s neighbor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16794X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16794X\"></sup>but blessed is the one who is kind to the needy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16794Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16794Y\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not those who plot evil go astray?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16795Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16795Z\"></sup>But those who plan what is good find love and faithfulness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>All hard work brings a profit,but mere talk leads only to poverty.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The wealth of the wise is their crown,but the folly of fools yields folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16797AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16797AA\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A truthful witness saves lives,but a false witness is deceitful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16798AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16798AB\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Whoever fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a secure fortress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16799AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16799AC\"></sup>and for their children it will be a refuge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16799AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16799AD\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a fountain of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16800AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16800AE\"></sup>turning a person from the snares of death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16800AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16800AF\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A large population is a king’s glory,but without subjects a prince is ruined.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16801AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16801AG\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Whoever is patient has great understanding,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16802AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16802AH\"></sup>but one who is quick-tempered displays folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16802AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16802AI\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>A heart at peace gives life to the body,but envy rots the bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16803AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16803AJ\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Whoever oppresses the poor shows contempt for their Maker,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16804AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16804AK\"></sup>but whoever is kind to the needy honors God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16804AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16804AL\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>When calamity comes, the wicked are brought down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16805AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16805AM\"></sup>but even in death the righteous seek refuge in God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16805AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16805AN\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Wisdom reposes in the heart of the discerning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16806AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16806AO\"></sup>and even among fools she lets herself be known.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Righteousness exalts a nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16807AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16807AP\"></sup>but sin condemns any people.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>A king delights in a wise servant,but a shameful servant arouses his fury.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16808AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16808AQ\"></sup>"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>A gentle answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16809A\"></sup> turns away wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16809B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16809B\"></sup>but a harsh word stirs up anger.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The tongue of the wise adorns knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16810C\"></sup>but the mouth of the fool gushes folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16810D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16810D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16811E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16811E\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are everywhere,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16811F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16811F\"></sup>keeping watch on the wicked and the good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16811G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16811G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The soothing tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16812H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16812H\"></sup> is a tree of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16812I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16812I\"></sup>but a perverse tongue crushes the spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16812J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16812J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A fool spurns a parent’s discipline,but whoever heeds correction shows prudence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16813K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16813K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The house of the righteous contains great treasure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16814L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16814L\"></sup>but the income of the wicked brings ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16814M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16814M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The lips of the wise spread knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16815N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16815N\"></sup>but the hearts of fools are not upright.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests the sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16816O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16816O\"></sup> of the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16816P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16816P\"></sup>but the prayer of the upright pleases him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16816Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16816Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests the way of the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16817R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16817R\"></sup>but he loves those who pursue righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16817S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16817S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Stern discipline awaits anyone who leaves the path;the one who hates correction will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16818T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16818T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Death and Destruction lie open before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16819U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16819U\"></sup>—how much more do human hearts!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16819V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16819V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Mockers resent correction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16820W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16820W\"></sup>so they avoid the wise.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A happy heart makes the face cheerful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16821X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16821X\"></sup>but heartache crushes the spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16821Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16821Y\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The discerning heart seeks knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16822Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16822Z\"></sup>but the mouth of a fool feeds on folly.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All the days of the oppressed are wretched,but the cheerful heart has a continual feast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16823AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16823AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Better a little with the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>than great wealth with turmoil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16824AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16824AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Better a small serving of vegetables with lovethan a fattened calf with hatred.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16825AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16825AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A hot-tempered person stirs up conflict,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16826AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16826AD\"></sup>but the one who is patient calms a quarrel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16826AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16826AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The way of the sluggard is blocked with thorns,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16827AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16827AF\"></sup>but the path of the upright is a highway.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A wise son brings joy to his father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16828AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16828AG\"></sup>but a foolish man despises his mother.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Folly brings joy to one who has no sense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16829AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16829AH\"></sup>but whoever has understanding keeps a straight course.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Plans fail for lack of counsel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16830AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16830AI\"></sup>but with many advisers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16830AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16830AJ\"></sup> they succeed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16830AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16830AK\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A person finds joy in giving an apt reply<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16831AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16831AL\"></sup>—and how good is a timely word!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16831AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16831AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The path of life leads upward for the prudentto keep them from going down to the realm of the dead.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> tears down the house of the proud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16833AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16833AN\"></sup>but he sets the widow’s boundary stones in place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16833AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16833AO\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests the thoughts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16834AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16834AP\"></sup> of the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16834AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16834AQ\"></sup>but gracious words are pure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16834AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16834AR\"></sup> in his sight.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The greedy bring ruin to their households,but the one who hates bribes will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16835AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16835AS\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The heart of the righteous weighs its answers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16836AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16836AT\"></sup>but the mouth of the wicked gushes evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16836AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16836AU\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is far from the wicked,but he hears the prayer of the righteous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16837AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16837AV\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Light in a messenger’s eyes brings joy to the heart,and good news gives health to the bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16838AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16838AW\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Whoever heeds life-giving correctionwill be at home among the wise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16839AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16839AX\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Those who disregard discipline despise themselves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16840AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16840AY\"></sup>but the one who heeds correction gains understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16840AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16840AZ\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Wisdom’s instruction is to fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16841BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16841BA\"></sup>and humility comes before honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16841BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16841BB\"></sup>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>To humans belong the plans of the heart,but from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comes the proper answer of the tongue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16842A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16842A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>All a person’s ways seem pure to them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16843B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16843B\"></sup>but motives are weighed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16843C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16843C\"></sup> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16843D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16843D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Commit to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> whatever you do,and he will establish your plans.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16844E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16844E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> works out everything to its proper end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16845F\"></sup>—even the wicked for a day of disaster.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16845G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16845G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests all the proud of heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16846H\"></sup>Be sure of this: They will not go unpunished.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16846I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Through love and faithfulness sin is atoned for;through the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16847J\"></sup> evil is avoided.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16847K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> takes pleasure in anyone’s way,he causes their enemies to make peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16848L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16848L\"></sup> with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16848M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16848M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Better a little with righteousnessthan much gain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16849N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16849N\"></sup> with injustice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16849O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16849O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In their hearts humans plan their course,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> establishes their steps.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16850P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16850P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The lips of a king speak as an oracle,and his mouth does not betray justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16851Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16851Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Honest scales and balances belong to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;all the weights in the bag are of his making.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16852R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16852R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Kings detest wrongdoing,for a throne is established through righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16853S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16853S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Kings take pleasure in honest lips;they value the one who speaks what is right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16854T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16854T\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>A king’s wrath is a messenger of death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16855U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16855U\"></sup>but the wise will appease it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16855V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16855V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When a king’s face brightens, it means life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16856W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16856W\"></sup>his favor is like a rain cloud in spring.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16856X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16856X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>How much better to get wisdom than gold,to get insight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16857Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16857Y\"></sup> rather than silver!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16857Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16857Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The highway of the upright avoids evil;those who guard their ways preserve their lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16858AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16858AA\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16859AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16859AB\"></sup> goes before destruction,a haughty spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16859AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16859AC\"></sup> before a fall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16859AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16859AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Better to be lowly in spirit along with the oppressedthan to share plunder with the proud.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Whoever gives heed to instruction prospers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16861AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16861AE\"></sup>and blessed is the one who trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16861AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16861AF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The wise in heart are called discerning,and gracious words promote instruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16862AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16862AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Prudence is a fountain of life to the prudent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16863AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16863AH\"></sup>but folly brings punishment to fools.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The hearts of the wise make their mouths prudent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16864AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16864AI\"></sup>and their lips promote instruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16864AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16864AJ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Gracious words are a honeycomb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16865AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16865AK\"></sup>sweet to the soul and healing to the bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16865AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16865AL\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>There is a way that appears to be right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16866AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16866AM\"></sup>but in the end it leads to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16866AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16866AN\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The appetite of laborers works for them;their hunger drives them on.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>A scoundrel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16868AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16868AO\"></sup> plots evil,and on their lips it is like a scorching fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16868AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16868AP\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A perverse person stirs up conflict,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16869AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16869AQ\"></sup>and a gossip separates close friends.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16869AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16869AR\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A violent person entices their neighborand leads them down a path that is not good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16870AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16870AS\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Whoever winks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16871AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16871AT\"></sup> with their eye is plotting perversity;whoever purses their lips is bent on evil.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Gray hair is a crown of splendor;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16872AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16872AU\"></sup>it is attained in the way of righteousness.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Better a patient person than a warrior,one with self-control than one who takes a city.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The lot is cast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16874AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16874AV\"></sup> into the lap,but its every decision<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16874AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16874AW\"></sup> is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16874AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16874AX\"></sup>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Better a dry crust with peace and quietthan a house full of feasting, with strife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16875A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16875A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A prudent servant will rule over a disgraceful sonand will share the inheritance as one of the family.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The crucible for silver and the furnace for gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16877B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16877B\"></sup>but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> tests the heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16877C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16877C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A wicked person listens to deceitful lips;a liar pays attention to a destructive tongue.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Whoever mocks the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16879D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16879D\"></sup> shows contempt for their Maker;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16879E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16879E\"></sup>whoever gloats over disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16879F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16879F\"></sup> will not go unpunished.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16879G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16879G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Children’s children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16880H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16880H\"></sup> are a crown to the aged,and parents are the pride of their children.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Eloquent lips are unsuited to a godless fool—how much worse lying lips to a ruler!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16881I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16881I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A bribe is seen as a charm by the one who gives it;they think success will come at every turn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16882J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16882J\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever would foster love covers over an offense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16883K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16883K\"></sup>but whoever repeats the matter separates close friends.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16883L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16883L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A rebuke impresses a discerning personmore than a hundred lashes a fool.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Evildoers foster rebellion against God;the messenger of death will be sent against them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Better to meet a bear robbed of her cubsthan a fool bent on folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16886M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16886M\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Evil will never leave the houseof one who pays back evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16887N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16887N\"></sup> for good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16887O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16887O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Starting a quarrel is like breaching a dam;so drop the matter before a dispute breaks out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16888P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16888P\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Acquitting the guilty and condemning the innocent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16889Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16889Q\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests them both.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16889R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16889R\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Why should fools have money in hand to buy wisdom,when they are not able to understand it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16890S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16890S\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A friend loves at all times,and a brother is born for a time of adversity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16891T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16891T\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>One who has no sense shakes hands in pledgeand puts up security for a neighbor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16892U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16892U\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Whoever loves a quarrel loves sin;whoever builds a high gate invites destruction.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>One whose heart is corrupt does not prosper;one whose tongue is perverse falls into trouble.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To have a fool for a child brings grief;there is no joy for the parent of a godless fool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16895V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16895V\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A cheerful heart is good medicine,but a crushed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16896W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16896W\"></sup> spirit dries up the bones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16896X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16896X\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The wicked accept bribes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16897Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16897Y\"></sup> in secretto pervert the course of justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16897Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16897Z\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A discerning person keeps wisdom in view,but a fool’s eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16898AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16898AA\"></sup> wander to the ends of the earth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A foolish son brings grief to his fatherand bitterness to the mother who bore him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16899AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16899AB\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If imposing a fine on the innocent is not good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16900AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16900AC\"></sup>surely to flog honest officials is not right.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The one who has knowledge uses words with restraint,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16901AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16901AD\"></sup>and whoever has understanding is even-tempered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16901AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16901AE\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Even fools are thought wise if they keep silent,and discerning if they hold their tongues.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16902AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16902AF\"></sup>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>An unfriendly person pursues selfish endsand against all sound judgment starts quarrels.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Fools find no pleasure in understandingbut delight in airing their own opinions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16904A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16904A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When wickedness comes, so does contempt,and with shame comes reproach.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The words of the mouth are deep waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16906B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16906B\"></sup>but the fountain of wisdom is a rushing stream.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It is not good to be partial to the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16907C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16907C\"></sup>and so deprive the innocent of justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16907D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16907D\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The lips of fools bring them strife,and their mouths invite a beating.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16908E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16908E\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The mouths of fools are their undoing,and their lips are a snare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16909F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16909F\"></sup> to their very lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16909G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16909G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The words of a gossip are like choice morsels;they go down to the inmost parts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16910H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16910H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>One who is slack in his workis brother to one who destroys.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16911I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16911I\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a fortified tower;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16912J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16912J\"></sup>the righteous run to it and are safe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16912K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16912K\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The wealth of the rich is their fortified city;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16913L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16913L\"></sup>they imagine it a wall too high to scale.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Before a downfall the heart is haughty,but humility comes before honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16914M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16914M\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>To answer before listening—that is folly and shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16915N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16915N\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The human spirit can endure in sickness,but a crushed spirit who can bear?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16916O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16916O\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The heart of the discerning acquires knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16917P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16917P\"></sup>for the ears of the wise seek it out.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A gift<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16918Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16918Q\"></sup> opens the wayand ushers the giver into the presence of the great.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In a lawsuit the first to speak seems right,until someone comes forward and cross-examines.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Casting the lot settles disputes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16920R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16920R\"></sup>and keeps strong opponents apart.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A brother wronged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16921S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16921S\"></sup> is more unyielding than a fortified city;disputes are like the barred gates of a citadel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>From the fruit of their mouth a person’s stomach is filled;with the harvest of their lips they are satisfied.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16922T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16922T\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The tongue has the power of life and death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16923U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16923U\"></sup>and those who love it will eat its fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16923V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16923V\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He who finds a wife finds what is good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16924W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16924W\"></sup>and receives favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16924X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16924X\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The poor plead for mercy,but the rich answer harshly.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>One who has unreliable friends soon comes to ruin,but there is a friend who sticks closer than a brother.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16926Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16926Y\"></sup>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Better the poor whose walk is blamelessthan a fool whose lips are perverse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16927A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16927A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Desire without knowledge is not good—how much more will hasty feet miss the way!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16928B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16928B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A person’s own folly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16929C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16929C\"></sup> leads to their ruin,yet their heart rages against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16929D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16929D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Wealth attracts many friends,but even the closest friend of the poor person deserts them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16930E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16930E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A false witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16931F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16931F\"></sup> will not go unpunished,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16931G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16931G\"></sup>and whoever pours out lies will not go free.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16931H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16931H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Many curry favor with a ruler,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16932I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16932I\"></sup>and everyone is the friend of one who gives gifts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16932J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16932J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The poor are shunned by all their relatives—how much more do their friends avoid them!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16933K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16933K\"></sup>Though the poor pursue them with pleading,they are nowhere to be found.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16933L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16933L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The one who gets wisdom loves life;the one who cherishes understanding will soon prosper.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16934M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16934M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A false witness will not go unpunished,and whoever pours out lies will perish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16935N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16935N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>It is not fitting for a fool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16936O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16936O\"></sup> to live in luxury—how much worse for a slave to rule over princes!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16936P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16936P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A person’s wisdom yields patience;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16937Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16937Q\"></sup>it is to one’s glory to overlook an offense.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A king’s rage is like the roar of a lion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16938R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16938R\"></sup>but his favor is like dew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16938S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16938S\"></sup> on the grass.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16938T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16938T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A foolish child is a father’s ruin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16939U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16939U\"></sup>and a quarrelsome wife is likethe constant dripping of a leaky roof.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16939V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16939V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Houses and wealth are inherited from parents,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16940W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16940W\"></sup>but a prudent wife is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16940X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16940X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Laziness brings on deep sleep,and the shiftless go hungry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16941Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16941Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Whoever keeps commandments keeps their life,but whoever shows contempt for their ways will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16942Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16942Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever is kind to the poor lends to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16943AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16943AA\"></sup>and he will reward them for what they have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16943AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16943AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Discipline your children, for in that there is hope;do not be a willing party to their death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16944AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16944AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A hot-tempered person must pay the penalty;rescue them, and you will have to do it again.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Listen to advice and accept discipline,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16946AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16946AD\"></sup>and at the end you will be counted among the wise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16946AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16946AE\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Many are the plans in a person’s heart,but it is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s purpose that prevails.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16947AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16947AF\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What a person desires is unfailing love;better to be poor than a liar.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> leads to life;then one rests content, untouched by trouble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16949AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16949AG\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A sluggard buries his hand in the dish;he will not even bring it back to his mouth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16950AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16950AH\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Flog a mocker, and the simple will learn prudence;rebuke the discerning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16951AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16951AI\"></sup> and they will gain knowledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16951AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16951AJ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Whoever robs their father and drives out their mother<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16952AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16952AK\"></sup>is a child who brings shame and disgrace.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Stop listening to instruction, my son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16953AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16953AL\"></sup>and you will stray from the words of knowledge.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A corrupt witness mocks at justice,and the mouth of the wicked gulps down evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16954AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16954AM\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Penalties are prepared for mockers,and beatings for the backs of fools.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16955AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16955AN\"></sup>"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16956A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16956A\"></sup> is a mocker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16956B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16956B\"></sup> and beer a brawler;whoever is led astray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16956C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16956C\"></sup> by them is not wise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16956D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16956D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A king’s wrath strikes terror like the roar of a lion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16957E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16957E\"></sup>those who anger him forfeit their lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16957F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16957F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It is to one’s honor to avoid strife,but every fool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16958G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16958G\"></sup> is quick to quarrel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16958H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16958H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Sluggards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16959I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16959I\"></sup> do not plow in season;so at harvest time they look but find nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16959J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16959J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The purposes of a person’s heart are deep waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16960K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16960K\"></sup>but one who has insight draws them out.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Many claim to have unfailing love,but a faithful person who can find?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16961L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16961L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The righteous lead blameless lives;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16962M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16962M\"></sup>blessed are their children after them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16962N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16962N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When a king sits on his throne to judge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16963O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16963O\"></sup>he winnows out all evil with his eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16963P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16963P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Who can say, “I have kept my heart pure;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16964Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16964Q\"></sup>I am clean and without sin”?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16964R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16964R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Differing weights and differing measures—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests them both.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16965S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16965S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Even small children are known by their actions,so is their conduct really pure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16966T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16966T\"></sup> and upright?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Ears that hear and eyes that see—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made them both.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16967U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16967U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not love sleep or you will grow poor;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16968V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16968V\"></sup>stay awake and you will have food to spare.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“It’s no good, it’s no good!” says the buyer—then goes off and boasts about the purchase.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Gold there is, and rubies in abundance,but lips that speak knowledge are a rare jewel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Take the garment of one who puts up security for a stranger;hold it in pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16971W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16971W\"></sup> if it is done for an outsider.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16971X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16971X\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Food gained by fraud tastes sweet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16972Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16972Y\"></sup>but one ends up with a mouth full of gravel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16972Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16972Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Plans are established by seeking advice;so if you wage war, obtain guidance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16973AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16973AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A gossip betrays a confidence;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16974AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16974AB\"></sup>so avoid anyone who talks too much.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If someone curses their father or mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16975AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16975AC\"></sup>their lamp will be snuffed out in pitch darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16975AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16975AD\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>An inheritance claimed too soonwill not be blessed at the end.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not say, “I’ll pay you back for this wrong!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16977AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16977AE\"></sup>Wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and he will avenge you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16977AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16977AF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> detests differing weights,and dishonest scales do not please him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16978AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16978AG\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A person’s steps are directed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16979AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16979AH\"></sup> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16979AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16979AI\"></sup>How then can anyone understand their own way?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16979AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16979AJ\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is a trap to dedicate something rashlyand only later to consider one’s vows.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16980AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16980AK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>A wise king winnows out the wicked;he drives the threshing wheel over them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16981AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16981AL\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The human spirit is the lamp of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16982AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16982AM\"></sup>that sheds light on one’s inmost being.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16982AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16982AN\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Love and faithfulness keep a king safe;through love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16983AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16983AO\"></sup> his throne is made secure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16983AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16983AP\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The glory of young men is their strength,gray hair the splendor of the old.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16984AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16984AQ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Blows and wounds scrub<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16985AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16985AR\"></sup> away evil,and beatings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16985AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16985AS\"></sup> purge the inmost being."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>In the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s hand the king’s heart is a stream of waterthat he channels toward all who please him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16986A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16986A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A person may think their own ways are right,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> weighs the heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16987B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16987B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To do what is right and justis more acceptable to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> than sacrifice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16988C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16988C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Haughty eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16989D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16989D\"></sup> and a proud heart—the unplowed field of the wicked—produce sin.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The plans of the diligent lead to profit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16990E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16990E\"></sup>as surely as haste leads to poverty.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A fortune made by a lying tongueis a fleeting vapor and a deadly snare.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16991F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16991F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The violence of the wicked will drag them away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16992G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16992G\"></sup>for they refuse to do what is right.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The way of the guilty is devious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16993H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16993H\"></sup>but the conduct of the innocent is upright.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Better to live on a corner of the roofthan share a house with a quarrelsome wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16994I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16994I\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The wicked crave evil;their neighbors get no mercy from them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When a mocker is punished, the simple gain wisdom;by paying attention to the wise they get knowledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16996J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16996J\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The Righteous One takes note of the house of the wickedand brings the wicked to ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16997K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16997K\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever shuts their ears to the cry of the poorwill also cry out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16998L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16998L\"></sup> and not be answered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16998M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16998M\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>A gift given in secret soothes anger,and a bribe concealed in the cloak pacifies great wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-16999N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-16999N\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When justice is done, it brings joy to the righteousbut terror to evildoers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17000O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17000O\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Whoever strays from the path of prudencecomes to rest in the company of the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17001P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17001P\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever loves pleasure will become poor;whoever loves wine and olive oil will never be rich.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17002Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17002Q\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wicked become a ransom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17003R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17003R\"></sup> for the righteous,and the unfaithful for the upright.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Better to live in a desertthan with a quarrelsome and nagging wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17004S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17004S\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The wise store up choice food and olive oil,but fools gulp theirs down.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Whoever pursues righteousness and lovefinds life, prosperity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17006T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17006T\"></sup> and honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17006U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17006U\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>One who is wise can go up against the city of the mighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17007V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17007V\"></sup>and pull down the stronghold in which they trust.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Those who guard their mouths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17008W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17008W\"></sup> and their tongueskeep themselves from calamity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17008X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17008X\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The proud and arrogant person<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17009Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17009Y\"></sup>—“Mocker” is his name—behaves with insolent fury.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The craving of a sluggard will be the death of him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17010Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17010Z\"></sup>because his hands refuse to work.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>All day long he craves for more,but the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17011AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17011AA\"></sup> give without sparing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17011AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17011AB\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The sacrifice of the wicked is detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17012AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17012AC\"></sup>—how much more so when brought with evil intent!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17012AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17012AD\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A false witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17013AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17013AE\"></sup> will perish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17013AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17013AF\"></sup>but a careful listener will testify successfully.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The wicked put up a bold front,but the upright give thought to their ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17014AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17014AG\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>There is no wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17015AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17015AH\"></sup> no insight, no planthat can succeed against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17015AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17015AI\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The horse is made ready for the day of battle,but victory rests with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17016AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17016AJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>A good name is more desirable than great riches;to be esteemed is better than silver or gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17017A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17017A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Rich and poor have this in common:The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the Maker of them all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17018B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The prudent see danger and take refuge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17019C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17019C\"></sup>but the simple keep going and pay the penalty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17019D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17019D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Humility is the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;its wages are riches and honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17020E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17020E\"></sup> and life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17020F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17020F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In the paths of the wicked are snares and pitfalls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17021G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17021G\"></sup>but those who would preserve their life stay far from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Start<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17022H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17022H\"></sup> children off on the way they should go,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17022I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17022I\"></sup>and even when they are old they will not turn from it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17022J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17022J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The rich rule over the poor,and the borrower is slave to the lender.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever sows injustice reaps calamity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17024K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17024K\"></sup>and the rod they wield in fury will be broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17024L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17024L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The generous will themselves be blessed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17025M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17025M\"></sup>for they share their food with the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17025N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17025N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Drive out the mocker, and out goes strife;quarrels and insults are ended.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17026O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17026O\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>One who loves a pure heart and who speaks with gracewill have the king for a friend.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17027P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17027P\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> keep watch over knowledge,but he frustrates the words of the unfaithful.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The sluggard says, “There’s a lion outside!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17029Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17029Q\"></sup>I’ll be killed in the public square!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The mouth of an adulterous woman is a deep pit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17030R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17030R\"></sup>a man who is under the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s wrath falls into it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17030S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17030S\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Folly is bound up in the heart of a child,but the rod of discipline will drive it far away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17031T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17031T\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>One who oppresses the poor to increase his wealthand one who gives gifts to the rich—both come to poverty.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Pay attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17033U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17033U\"></sup> and turn your ear to the sayings of the wise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17033V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17033V\"></sup>apply your heart to what I teach,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17033W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17033W\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for it is pleasing when you keep them in your heartand have all of them ready on your lips.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So that your trust may be in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,I teach you today, even you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Have I not written thirty sayings for you,sayings of counsel and knowledge,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>teaching you to be honest and to speak the truth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17037X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17037X\"></sup>so that you bring back truthful reportsto those you serve?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not exploit the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17038Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17038Y\"></sup> because they are poorand do not crush the needy in court,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17038Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17038Z\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will take up their case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17039AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17039AA\"></sup>and will exact life for life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17039AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17039AB\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Do not make friends with a hot-tempered person,do not associate with one easily angered,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>or you may learn their waysand get yourself ensnared.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17041AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17041AC\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Do not be one who shakes hands in pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17042AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17042AD\"></sup>or puts up security for debts;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>if you lack the means to pay,your very bed will be snatched from under you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17043AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17043AE\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not move an ancient boundary stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17044AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17044AF\"></sup>set up by your ancestors.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do you see someone skilled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17045AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17045AG\"></sup> in their work?They will serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17045AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17045AH\"></sup> before kings;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17045AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17045AI\"></sup>they will not serve before officials of low rank."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>When you sit to dine with a ruler,note well what is before you,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and put a knife to your throatif you are given to gluttony.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not crave his delicacies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17048A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17048A\"></sup>for that food is deceptive.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do not wear yourself out to get rich;do not trust your own cleverness.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Cast but a glance at riches, and they are gone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17050B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17050B\"></sup>for they will surely sprout wingsand fly off to the sky like an eagle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17050C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17050C\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not eat the food of a begrudging host,do not crave his delicacies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17051D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17051D\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for he is the kind of personwho is always thinking about the cost.“Eat and drink,” he says to you,but his heart is not with you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You will vomit up the little you have eatenand will have wasted your compliments.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not speak to fools,for they will scorn your prudent words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17054E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17054E\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not move an ancient boundary stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17055F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17055F\"></sup>or encroach on the fields of the fatherless,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>for their Defender<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17056G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17056G\"></sup> is strong;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17056H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17056H\"></sup>he will take up their case against you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17056I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17056I\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Apply your heart to instruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17057J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17057J\"></sup>and your ears to words of knowledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not withhold discipline from a child;if you punish them with the rod, they will not die.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Punish them with the rodand save them from death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17059K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17059K\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>My son, if your heart is wise,then my heart will be glad indeed;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>my inmost being will rejoicewhen your lips speak what is right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17061L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17061L\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not let your heart envy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17062M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17062M\"></sup> sinners,but always be zealous for the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There is surely a future hope for you,and your hope will not be cut off.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17063N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17063N\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Listen, my son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17064O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17064O\"></sup> and be wise,and set your heart on the right path:",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do not join those who drink too much wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17065P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17065P\"></sup>or gorge themselves on meat,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for drunkards and gluttons become poor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17066Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17066Q\"></sup>and drowsiness clothes them in rags.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Listen to your father, who gave you life,and do not despise your mother when she is old.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17067R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17067R\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Buy the truth and do not sell it—wisdom, instruction and insight as well.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17068S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17068S\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The father of a righteous child has great joy;a man who fathers a wise son rejoices in him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17069T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17069T\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>May your father and mother rejoice;may she who gave you birth be joyful!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17070U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17070U\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>My son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17071V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17071V\"></sup> give me your heartand let your eyes delight in my ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17071W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17071W\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>for an adulterous woman is a deep pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17072X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17072X\"></sup>and a wayward wife is a narrow well.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Like a bandit she lies in wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17073Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17073Y\"></sup>and multiplies the unfaithful among men.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Who has woe? Who has sorrow?Who has strife? Who has complaints?Who has needless bruises? Who has bloodshot eyes?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Those who linger over wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17075Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17075Z\"></sup>who go to sample bowls of mixed wine.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Do not gaze at wine when it is red,when it sparkles in the cup,when it goes down smoothly!",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>In the end it bites like a snakeand poisons like a viper.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Your eyes will see strange sights,and your mind will imagine confusing things.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>You will be like one sleeping on the high seas,lying on top of the rigging.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“They hit me,” you will say, “but I’m not hurt!They beat me, but I don’t feel it!When will I wake upso I can find another drink?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17080AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17080AA\"></sup>"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>Do not envy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17081A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17081A\"></sup> the wicked,do not desire their company;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for their hearts plot violence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17082B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17082B\"></sup>and their lips talk about making trouble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17082C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By wisdom a house is built,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17083D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17083D\"></sup>and through understanding it is established;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>through knowledge its rooms are filledwith rare and beautiful treasures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17084E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17084E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The wise prevail through great power,and those who have knowledge muster their strength.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Surely you need guidance to wage war,and victory is won through many advisers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17086F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17086F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Wisdom is too high for fools;in the assembly at the gate they must not open their mouths.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever plots evilwill be known as a schemer.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The schemes of folly are sin,and people detest a mocker.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If you falter in a time of trouble,how small is your strength!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17090G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17090G\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Rescue those being led away to death;hold back those staggering toward slaughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17091H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17091H\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you say, “But we knew nothing about this,”does not he who weighs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17092I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17092I\"></sup> the heart perceive it?Does not he who guards your life know it?Will he not repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17092J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17092J\"></sup> everyone according to what they have done?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17092K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17092K\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Eat honey, my son, for it is good;honey from the comb is sweet to your taste.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Know also that wisdom is like honey for you:If you find it, there is a future hope for you,and your hope will not be cut off.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17094L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17094L\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do not lurk like a thief near the house of the righteous,do not plunder their dwelling place;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for though the righteous fall seven times, they rise again,but the wicked stumble when calamity strikes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17096M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17096M\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not gloat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17097N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17097N\"></sup> when your enemy falls;when they stumble, do not let your heart rejoice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17097O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17097O\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>or the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will see and disapproveand turn his wrath away from them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17098P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17098P\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not fret<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17099Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17099Q\"></sup> because of evildoersor be envious of the wicked,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for the evildoer has no future hope,and the lamp of the wicked will be snuffed out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17100R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17100R\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the king,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17101S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17101S\"></sup> my son,and do not join with rebellious officials,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for those two will send sudden destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17102T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17102T\"></sup> on them,and who knows what calamities they can bring?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>These also are sayings of the wise:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17103U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17103U\"></sup>To show partiality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17103V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17103V\"></sup> in judging is not good:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17103W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17103W\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever says to the guilty, “You are innocent,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17104X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17104X\"></sup>will be cursed by peoples and denounced by nations.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But it will go well with those who convict the guilty,and rich blessing will come on them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>An honest answeris like a kiss on the lips.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Put your outdoor work in orderand get your fields ready;after that, build your house.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not testify against your neighbor without cause<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17108Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17108Y\"></sup>—would you use your lips to mislead?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do not say, “I’ll do to them as they have done to me;I’ll pay them back for what they did.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17109Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17109Z\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I went past the field of a sluggard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17110AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17110AA\"></sup>past the vineyard of someone who has no sense;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>thorns had come up everywhere,the ground was covered with weeds,and the stone wall was in ruins.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>I applied my heart to what I observedand learned a lesson from what I saw:",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>A little sleep, a little slumber,a little folding of the hands to rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17113AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17113AB\"></sup>—",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>and poverty will come on you like a thiefand scarcity like an armed man.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17114AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17114AC\"></sup>"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>These are more proverbs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17115A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17115A\"></sup> of Solomon, compiled by the men of Hezekiah king of Judah:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17115B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17115B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It is the glory of God to conceal a matter;to search out a matter is the glory of kings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17116C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17116C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As the heavens are high and the earth is deep,so the hearts of kings are unsearchable.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Remove the dross from the silver,and a silversmith can produce a vessel;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>remove wicked officials from the king’s presence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17119D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17119D\"></sup>and his throne will be established<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17119E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17119E\"></sup> through righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17119F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17119F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not exalt yourself in the king’s presence,and do not claim a place among his great men;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>it is better for him to say to you, “Come up here,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17121G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17121G\"></sup>than for him to humiliate you before his nobles.What you have seen with your eyes",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>do not bring hastily to court,for what will you do in the endif your neighbor puts you to shame?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17122H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17122H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If you take your neighbor to court,do not betray another’s confidence,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>or the one who hears it may shame youand the charge against you will stand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like apples of gold in settings of silver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17125I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17125I\"></sup>is a ruling rightly given.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Like an earring of gold or an ornament of fine goldis the rebuke of a wise judge to a listening ear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17126J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17126J\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Like a snow-cooled drink at harvest timeis a trustworthy messenger to the one who sends him;he refreshes the spirit of his master.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17127K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17127K\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Like clouds and wind without rainis one who boasts of gifts never given.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Through patience a ruler can be persuaded,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17129L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17129L\"></sup>and a gentle tongue can break a bone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17129M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17129M\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If you find honey, eat just enough—too much of it, and you will vomit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17130N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17130N\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Seldom set foot in your neighbor’s house—too much of you, and they will hate you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Like a club or a sword or a sharp arrowis one who gives false testimony against a neighbor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17132O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17132O\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Like a broken tooth or a lame footis reliance on the unfaithful in a time of trouble.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Like one who takes away a garment on a cold day,or like vinegar poured on a wound,is one who sings songs to a heavy heart.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>If your enemy is hungry, give him food to eat;if he is thirsty, give him water to drink.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In doing this, you will heap burning coals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17136P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17136P\"></sup> on his head,and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will reward you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17136Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17136Q\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Like a north wind that brings unexpected rainis a sly tongue—which provokes a horrified look.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Better to live on a corner of the roofthan share a house with a quarrelsome wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17138R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17138R\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Like cold water to a weary soulis good news from a distant land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17139S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17139S\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Like a muddied spring or a polluted wellare the righteous who give way to the wicked.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>It is not good to eat too much honey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17141T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17141T\"></sup>nor is it honorable to search out matters that are too deep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17141U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17141U\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Like a city whose walls are broken throughis a person who lacks self-control."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Like snow in summer or rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17143A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17143A\"></sup> in harvest,honor is not fitting for a fool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17143B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17143B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like a fluttering sparrow or a darting swallow,an undeserved curse does not come to rest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17144C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17144C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A whip for the horse, a bridle for the donkey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17145D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17145D\"></sup>and a rod for the backs of fools!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17145E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17145E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do not answer a fool according to his folly,or you yourself will be just like him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17146F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17146F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Answer a fool according to his folly,or he will be wise in his own eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17147G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17147G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Sending a message by the hands of a fool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17148H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17148H\"></sup>is like cutting off one’s feet or drinking poison.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Like the useless legs of one who is lameis a proverb in the mouth of a fool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17149I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17149I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like tying a stone in a slingis the giving of honor to a fool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17150J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17150J\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Like a thornbush in a drunkard’s handis a proverb in the mouth of a fool.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17151K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17151K\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Like an archer who wounds at randomis one who hires a fool or any passer-by.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As a dog returns to its vomit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17153L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17153L\"></sup>so fools repeat their folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17153M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17153M\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do you see a person wise in their own eyes?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17154N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17154N\"></sup>There is more hope for a fool than for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17154O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17154O\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>A sluggard says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17155P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17155P\"></sup> “There’s a lion in the road,a fierce lion roaming the streets!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17155Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17155Q\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As a door turns on its hinges,so a sluggard turns on his bed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17156R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17156R\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A sluggard buries his hand in the dish;he is too lazy to bring it back to his mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17157S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17157S\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A sluggard is wiser in his own eyesthan seven people who answer discreetly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Like one who grabs a stray dog by the earsis someone who rushes into a quarrel not their own.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Like a maniac shootingflaming arrows of death",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>is one who deceives their neighborand says, “I was only joking!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Without wood a fire goes out;without a gossip a quarrel dies down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17162T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17162T\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>As charcoal to embers and as wood to fire,so is a quarrelsome person for kindling strife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17163U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17163U\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The words of a gossip are like choice morsels;they go down to the inmost parts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17164V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17164V\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Like a coating of silver dross on earthenwareare fervent lips with an evil heart.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Enemies disguise themselves with their lips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17166W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17166W\"></sup>but in their hearts they harbor deceit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17166X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17166X\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Though their speech is charming,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17167Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17167Y\"></sup> do not believe them,for seven abominations fill their hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17167Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17167Z\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Their malice may be concealed by deception,but their wickedness will be exposed in the assembly.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whoever digs a pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17169AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17169AA\"></sup> will fall into it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17169AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17169AB\"></sup>if someone rolls a stone, it will roll back on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17169AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17169AC\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A lying tongue hates those it hurts,and a flattering mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17170AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17170AD\"></sup> works ruin."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>Do not boast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17171A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17171A\"></sup> about tomorrow,for you do not know what a day may bring.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17171B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17171B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let someone else praise you, and not your own mouth;an outsider, and not your own lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17172C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17172C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Stone is heavy and sand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17173D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17173D\"></sup> a burden,but a fool’s provocation is heavier than both.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Anger is cruel and fury overwhelming,but who can stand before jealousy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17174E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17174E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Better is open rebukethan hidden love.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Wounds from a friend can be trusted,but an enemy multiplies kisses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17176F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17176F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>One who is full loathes honey from the comb,but to the hungry even what is bitter tastes sweet.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like a bird that flees its nest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17178G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17178G\"></sup>is anyone who flees from home.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Perfume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17179H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17179H\"></sup> and incense bring joy to the heart,and the pleasantness of a friendsprings from their heartfelt advice.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not forsake your friend or a friend of your family,and do not go to your relative’s house when disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17180I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17180I\"></sup> strikes you—better a neighbor nearby than a relative far away.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Be wise, my son, and bring joy to my heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17181J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17181J\"></sup>then I can answer anyone who treats me with contempt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17181K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17181K\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The prudent see danger and take refuge,but the simple keep going and pay the penalty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17182L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17182L\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Take the garment of one who puts up security for a stranger;hold it in pledge if it is done for an outsider.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17183M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17183M\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If anyone loudly blesses their neighbor early in the morning,it will be taken as a curse.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A quarrelsome wife is like the dripping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17185N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17185N\"></sup>of a leaky roof in a rainstorm;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>restraining her is like restraining the windor grasping oil with the hand.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As iron sharpens iron,so one person sharpens another.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The one who guards a fig tree will eat its fruit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17188O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17188O\"></sup>and whoever protects their master will be honored.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17188P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17188P\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As water reflects the face,so one’s life reflects the heart.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Death and Destruction are never satisfied,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17190Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17190Q\"></sup>and neither are human eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17190R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17190R\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The crucible for silver and the furnace for gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17191S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17191S\"></sup>but people are tested by their praise.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Though you grind a fool in a mortar,grinding them like grain with a pestle,you will not remove their folly from them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Be sure you know the condition of your flocks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17193T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17193T\"></sup>give careful attention to your herds;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for riches do not endure forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17194U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17194U\"></sup>and a crown is not secure for all generations.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When the hay is removed and new growth appearsand the grass from the hills is gathered in,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>the lambs will provide you with clothing,and the goats with the price of a field.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You will have plenty of goats’ milk to feed your familyand to nourish your female servants."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>The wicked flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17198A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17198A\"></sup> though no one pursues,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17198B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17198B\"></sup>but the righteous are as bold as a lion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17198C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17198C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When a country is rebellious, it has many rulers,but a ruler with discernment and knowledge maintains order.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A ruler who oppresses the pooris like a driving rain that leaves no crops.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Those who forsake instruction praise the wicked,but those who heed it resist them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Evildoers do not understand what is right,but those who seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> understand it fully.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Better the poor whose walk is blamelessthan the rich whose ways are perverse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17203D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17203D\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A discerning son heeds instruction,but a companion of gluttons disgraces his father.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17204E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17204E\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever increases wealth by taking interest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17205F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17205F\"></sup> or profit from the pooramasses it for another,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17205G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17205G\"></sup> who will be kind to the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17205H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17205H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If anyone turns a deaf ear to my instruction,even their prayers are detestable.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17206I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17206I\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever leads the upright along an evil pathwill fall into their own trap,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17207J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17207J\"></sup>but the blameless will receive a good inheritance.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The rich are wise in their own eyes;one who is poor and discerning sees how deluded they are.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When the righteous triumph, there is great elation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17209K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17209K\"></sup>but when the wicked rise to power, people go into hiding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17209L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17209L\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever conceals their sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17210M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17210M\"></sup> does not prosper,but the one who confesses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17210N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17210N\"></sup> and renounces them finds mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17210O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17210O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Blessed is the one who always trembles before God,but whoever hardens their heart falls into trouble.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Like a roaring lion or a charging bearis a wicked ruler over a helpless people.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A tyrannical ruler practices extortion,but one who hates ill-gotten gain will enjoy a long reign.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Anyone tormented by the guilt of murderwill seek refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17214P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17214P\"></sup> in the grave;let no one hold them back.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The one whose walk is blameless is kept safe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17215Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17215Q\"></sup>but the one whose ways are perverse will fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17215R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17215R\"></sup> into the pit.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Those who work their land will have abundant food,but those who chase fantasies will have their fill of poverty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17216S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17216S\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A faithful person will be richly blessed,but one eager to get rich will not go unpunished.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17217T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17217T\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To show partiality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17218U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17218U\"></sup> is not good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17218V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17218V\"></sup>—yet a person will do wrong for a piece of bread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17218W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17218W\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The stingy are eager to get richand are unaware that poverty awaits them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17219X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17219X\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Whoever rebukes a person will in the end gain favorrather than one who has a flattering tongue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17220Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17220Y\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever robs their father or mother<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17221Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17221Z\"></sup>and says, “It’s not wrong,”is partner to one who destroys.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17221AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17221AA\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The greedy stir up conflict,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17222AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17222AB\"></sup>but those who trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17222AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17222AC\"></sup> will prosper.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Those who trust in themselves are fools,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17223AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17223AD\"></sup>but those who walk in wisdom are kept safe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17223AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17223AE\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Those who give to the poor will lack nothing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17224AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17224AF\"></sup>but those who close their eyes to them receive many curses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17224AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17224AG\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When the wicked rise to power, people go into hiding;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17225AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17225AH\"></sup>but when the wicked perish, the righteous thrive."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>Whoever remains stiff-necked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17226A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17226A\"></sup> after many rebukeswill suddenly be destroyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17226B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17226B\"></sup>—without remedy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17226C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17226C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the righteous thrive, the people rejoice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17227D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17227D\"></sup>when the wicked rule,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17227E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17227E\"></sup> the people groan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17227F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17227F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A man who loves wisdom brings joy to his father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17228G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17228G\"></sup>but a companion of prostitutes squanders his wealth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17228H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17228H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By justice a king gives a country stability,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17229I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17229I\"></sup>but those who are greedy for bribes tear it down.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who flatter their neighborsare spreading nets for their feet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17230J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17230J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Evildoers are snared by their own sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17231K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17231K\"></sup>but the righteous shout for joy and are glad.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The righteous care about justice for the poor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17232L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17232L\"></sup>but the wicked have no such concern.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Mockers stir up a city,but the wise turn away anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17233M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17233M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If a wise person goes to court with a fool,the fool rages and scoffs, and there is no peace.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The bloodthirsty hate a person of integrityand seek to kill the upright.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17235N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17235N\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Fools give full vent to their rage,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17236O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17236O\"></sup>but the wise bring calm in the end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17236P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17236P\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If a ruler<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17237Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17237Q\"></sup> listens to lies,all his officials become wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17237R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17237R\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The poor and the oppressor have this in common:The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives sight to the eyes of both.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17238S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17238S\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If a king judges the poor with fairness,his throne will be established forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17239T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17239T\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A rod and a reprimand impart wisdom,but a child left undisciplined disgraces its mother.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17240U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17240U\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When the wicked thrive, so does sin,but the righteous will see their downfall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17241V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17241V\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Discipline your children, and they will give you peace;they will bring you the delights you desire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17242W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17242W\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Where there is no revelation, people cast off restraint;but blessed is the one who heeds wisdom’s instruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17243X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17243X\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Servants cannot be corrected by mere words;though they understand, they will not respond.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do you see someone who speaks in haste?There is more hope for a fool than for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17245Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17245Y\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A servant pampered from youthwill turn out to be insolent.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>An angry person stirs up conflict,and a hot-tempered person commits many sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17247Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17247Z\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Pride brings a person low,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17248AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17248AA\"></sup>but the lowly in spirit gain honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17248AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17248AB\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The accomplices of thieves are their own enemies;they are put under oath and dare not testify.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17249AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17249AC\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17250AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17250AD\"></sup> of man will prove to be a snare,but whoever trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17250AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17250AE\"></sup> is kept safe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17250AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17250AF\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Many seek an audience with a ruler,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17251AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17251AG\"></sup>but it is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that one gets justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17251AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17251AH\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The righteous detest the dishonest;the wicked detest the upright.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17252AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17252AI\"></sup>"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The sayings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17253A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17253A\"></sup> of Agur son of Jakeh—an inspired utterance.This man’s utterance to Ithiel:“I am weary, God,but I can prevail.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely I am only a brute, not a man;I do not have human understanding.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I have not learned wisdom,nor have I attained to the knowledge of the Holy One.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17255B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17255B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who has gone up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17256C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17256C\"></sup> to heaven and come down?Whose hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17256D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17256D\"></sup> have gathered up the wind?Who has wrapped up the waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17256E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17256E\"></sup> in a cloak?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17256F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17256F\"></sup>Who has established all the ends of the earth?What is his name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17256G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17256G\"></sup> and what is the name of his son?Surely you know!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Every word of God is flawless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17257H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17257H\"></sup>he is a shield<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17257I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17257I\"></sup> to those who take refuge in him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not add<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17258J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17258J\"></sup> to his words,or he will rebuke you and prove you a liar.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Two things I ask of you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;do not refuse me before I die:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Keep falsehood and lies far from me;give me neither poverty nor riches,but give me only my daily bread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17260K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17260K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Otherwise, I may have too much and disown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17261L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17261L\"></sup> youand say, ‘Who is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17261M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17261M\"></sup>Or I may become poor and steal,and so dishonor the name of my God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17261N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17261N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Do not slander a servant to their master,or they will curse you, and you will pay for it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“There are those who curse their fathersand do not bless their mothers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17263O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17263O\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>those who are pure in their own eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17264P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17264P\"></sup>and yet are not cleansed of their filth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17264Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17264Q\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>those whose eyes are ever so haughty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17265R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17265R\"></sup>whose glances are so disdainful;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>those whose teeth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17266S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17266S\"></sup> are swordsand whose jaws are set with knives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17266T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17266T\"></sup>to devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17266U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17266U\"></sup> the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17266V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17266V\"></sup> from the earthand the needy from among mankind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17266W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17266W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The leech has two daughters.‘Give! Give!’ they cry.“There are three things that are never satisfied,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17267X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17267X\"></sup>four that never say, ‘Enough!’:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>the grave,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17268Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17268Y\"></sup> the barren womb,land, which is never satisfied with water,and fire, which never says, ‘Enough!’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“The eye that mocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17269Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17269Z\"></sup> a father,that scorns an aged mother,will be pecked out by the ravens of the valley,will be eaten by the vultures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17269AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17269AA\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“There are three things that are too amazing for me,four that I do not understand:",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the way of an eagle in the sky,the way of a snake on a rock,the way of a ship on the high seas,and the way of a man with a young woman.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“This is the way of an adulterous woman:She eats and wipes her mouthand says, ‘I’ve done nothing wrong.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17272AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17272AB\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Under three things the earth trembles,under four it cannot bear up:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>a servant who becomes king,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17274AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17274AC\"></sup>a godless fool who gets plenty to eat,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>a contemptible woman who gets married,and a servant who displaces her mistress.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Four things on earth are small,yet they are extremely wise:",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Ants are creatures of little strength,yet they store up their food in the summer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17277AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17277AD\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>hyraxes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17278AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17278AE\"></sup> are creatures of little power,yet they make their home in the crags;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17279AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17279AF\"></sup> have no king,yet they advance together in ranks;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>a lizard can be caught with the hand,yet it is found in kings’ palaces.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“There are three things that are stately in their stride,four that move with stately bearing:",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>a lion, mighty among beasts,who retreats before nothing;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>a strutting rooster, a he-goat,and a king secure against revolt.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“If you play the fool and exalt yourself,or if you plan evil,clap your hand over your mouth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17284AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17284AG\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For as churning cream produces butter,and as twisting the nose produces blood,so stirring up anger produces strife.”"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>The sayings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17286A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17286A\"></sup> of King Lemuel—an inspired utterance his mother taught him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Listen, my son! Listen, son of my womb!Listen, my son, the answer to my prayers!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17287B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17287B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not spend your strength on women,your vigor on those who ruin kings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17288C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17288C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It is not for kings, Lemuel—it is not for kings to drink wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17289D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17289D\"></sup>not for rulers to crave beer,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>lest they drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17290E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17290E\"></sup> and forget what has been decreed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17290F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17290F\"></sup>and deprive all the oppressed of their rights.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Let beer be for those who are perishing,wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17291G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17291G\"></sup> for those who are in anguish!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Let them drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17292H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17292H\"></sup> and forget their povertyand remember their misery no more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Speak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17293I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17293I\"></sup> up for those who cannot speak for themselves,for the rights of all who are destitute.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Speak up and judge fairly;defend the rights of the poor and needy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17294J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17294J\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A wife of noble character<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17295K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17295K\"></sup> who can find?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17295L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17295L\"></sup>She is worth far more than rubies.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Her husband<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17296M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17296M\"></sup> has full confidence in herand lacks nothing of value.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17296N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17296N\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>She brings him good, not harm,all the days of her life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She selects wool and flaxand works with eager hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17298O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17298O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She is like the merchant ships,bringing her food from afar.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>She gets up while it is still night;she provides food for her familyand portions for her female servants.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>She considers a field and buys it;out of her earnings she plants a vineyard.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>She sets about her work vigorously;her arms are strong for her tasks.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She sees that her trading is profitable,and her lamp does not go out at night.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In her hand she holds the distaffand grasps the spindle with her fingers.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>She opens her arms to the poorand extends her hands to the needy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17305P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17305P\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When it snows, she has no fear for her household;for all of them are clothed in scarlet.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>She makes coverings for her bed;she is clothed in fine linen and purple.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Her husband is respected at the city gate,where he takes his seat among the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17308Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17308Q\"></sup> of the land.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>She makes linen garments and sells them,and supplies the merchants with sashes.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>She is clothed with strength and dignity;she can laugh at the days to come.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>She speaks with wisdom,and faithful instruction is on her tongue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17311R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17311R\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She watches over the affairs of her householdand does not eat the bread of idleness.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Her children arise and call her blessed;her husband also, and he praises her:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Many women do noble things,but you surpass them all.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Charm is deceptive, and beauty is fleeting;but a woman who fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is to be praised.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Honor her for all that her hands have done,and let her works bring her praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17316S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17316S\"></sup> at the city gate."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;